com.nus.cool.core.cohort.birthselect

Class BirthContextWindow

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.nus.cool.core.cohort.birthselect.BirthContextWindow

  • public class BirthContextWindow
extends java.lang.Object
    BirthContextWindow is a sliding window based on adaptive queue. It keep a maxTimeWindow and a time-based queue (LinkedList) When new (eventId, datetime) input, this queue will automatically pop elements to keep the time duration between the first and the last element is less than the maxTimeWindow
